  Source:
    Title: Apastamba Dharma Sutra
    Locus: I i 15-18
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
---
Never should (a student) think ill of him (the teacher). For the
teacher gives him a (new) birth in knowledge. And that is the highest
birth. Mother and father engender his body only.
